This paper deals with deep learning models and their optimization, which is a common topic in the machine learning community. The paper specifically focuses on knowledge transfer between different models, which is a subfield of transfer learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also mentions reinforcement learning, which falls under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and natural language processing, which falls under cs.CL (Computation and Language).
